    <div class="body">
        <p>AbstractTableGateway class extends TableGatewayInterface, it should extend definitions methods as well</p>

<p>But TableGatewayInterface::update looks like this:</p>

<blockquote>
  <blockquote>
    <p>public function update($set, $where = null);</p>
  </blockquote>
</blockquote>

<p>and AbstractTableGateway::update like this:</p>

<blockquote>
  <blockquote>
    <p>public function update($set, $where)
       {
           $this-&gt;initialize();
           return parent::update($set, $where);
       }</p>
  </blockquote>
</blockquote>

